title: Top 30 Country + Recurrents May 6, 2014
description:
Only one song debuts on the chart this week (Swon Brothers) so I decided to include a list of songs which had been on the charts at some point this year but are now Recurrent, which means these are recent songs but no longer on the current country chart.  I also included some of the more familiar radio versions instead of the album cuts.  23 recurrents plus this week's Top 30 U.S. Country Singles as ranked by Mediabase makes this the largest torrent posted to date (over 3 hours of hot country music)!

Here are the Top 30 Country songs for the week of May 6, 2014 with their chart positions and effective broadcast run time.  Hope you like them!
